source.name: Prescribed Fires and Acres from 1998 to 2008 by Agency
source.description: Number of prescribed fires and acres, from 1998 through 2008 (updated annually). Displayed by the five federal land managing agencies and state/local entities.  This information is supplied by the Department of Interior and the Department of Agriculture.
